title: Wrap Org Mode Task State Changes Into a Drawer
tags: @zettel _method emacs orgmode
roam-id: 85f5bd83-0ca3-4bef-8779-49ac9268efee
type: text/markdown

- I watched this video for the solution <https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L0EJeN1fCYw&pp=ygUVZW1hY3MgcHJvdCBvcmctYWdlbmRh>

- put the following into your emacs config

  ``` commonlisp
  (setq org-log-into-drawer t) ;; wrap org mode task state changes into a drawer
  ```
